tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE market_sentiment_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    sentiment_score FLOAT,
    trade_strategy VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    asset_name VARCHAR(50),
    trade_type VARCHAR(10),
    trade_amount FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT,
    stock_symbol TEXT,
    trade_type TEXT,
    trade_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_id INT,
    buy_sell VARCHAR(4),
    amount FLOAT,
    timestamp timestamp
);
